                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130915-138-off801 t18130915-138-crimeloc804"></join>; I went up stairs to ask my wife if breakfast was ready, and returning to the place the padlock was gone; I went after the prisoner, and found her in Short's-garden's; I laid hold of the prisoner; she threw the padlock away. She had only come out of prison the day before.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Please your honour, I was going up Bow-street, I saw a parcel of rags and bones, I pick them up to get my living.</p>
